{
  "stem": "18102.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everyone used the cemetery as a quick way to get into town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But curfew was at 6:00 PM.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one evening as I was looking through my peephole upstairs in a window, I saw a young girl-- she had to be in her teens, maybe 17, maybe 18, maybe 16-- leave for the, the shortcut.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I realized that it was near curfew, and she was rushing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she had her head down as if that way she won't be detected.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I saw two soldiers-- German soldiers-- see her go into the cemetery, and they took after her.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They caught her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I, of course, didn't know at the time that it was a rape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't know what rape meant until years later, but that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's what I witnessed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I witnessed her scream and the soldiers jump on her, hold her down, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that memory, of course, haunted me [SIGHS] in later years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Of course, I had heard the girl scream, and so I knew it was violent.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't quite know exactly what it was, but I knew it wasn't pleasant for her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the scream and her fear transmitted to me, and I'm, as I say, was haunted for that for many years.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I would remember it--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in nightmares.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never saw that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was near nightfall, and I never saw what happened afterwards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think she was killed because there was nothing in the morning to indicate that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I really think it was just the rape and nothing more, as if you can say nothing more, but that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that is something that I did experience on a personal level watching, but I didn't see any other physical [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] injuries.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
